{"tid":2430841,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"300萬個體戶疫市執笠  小店轉營淫業 老闆走佬避債","createTime":"2021-03-03T08:20:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-03T10:10:15.000Z","uid":25558,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"83e05cda7c4e63c5b604603bf9968bad9b092217","tid":2430841,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T08:20:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210303/MWUAHBI3L5EMRD4R5J62C2D6LE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210303%2FMWUAHBI3L5EMRD4R5J62C2D6LE%2F&d=uMWHtpimsJ%2FyHBgDjrBiulLn0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=662598c4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210303%2FMWUAHBI3L5EMRD4R5J62C2D6LE%2F&h=9ab6cdd8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210303/MWUAHBI3L5EMRD4R5J62C2D6LE/</a><br />\n<br />\n300萬個體戶疫市執笠 <br />\n小店轉營淫業 老闆走佬避債<br />\n<br />\n【通街拉閘】內地個體戶小店疫情下出現結業潮。數據顯示，去年1月至11月內地共吊銷、註銷逾300萬個體戶及私人公司。內地有企業數據分析師估計，其中倒閉的小店、店舖多達過百萬間。經濟學者徐家健向本報分析指，個體小商戶大量結業，反映內地受網購興起及疫情影響，生意模式轉型，未來經濟的實際走勢是否轉差，還需留意其後新註冊商戶數量。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：京男打國藥疫苗發高燒出紅疹<br />\n<br />\n疫情下，官方公佈去年全年國內生產總值（GDP）增長仍有2.3%，但個體戶結業潮，卻為國內經濟響起警號。內地企業資料查詢網站。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/sWvQJamJ19ZMivUIU07UJ4KoZ_Q=/3150x2100/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3UBYF6E3WRDZ3GQ6BUL5NQUPXA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FsWvQJamJ19ZMivUIU07UJ4KoZ_Q%3D%2F3150x2100%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3UBYF6E3WRDZ3GQ6BUL5NQUPXA.jpg&h=2bc34bfd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【廣州】■三元里多間小店倒閉。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n健身洗浴衝擊最大<br />\n<br />\n內媒走訪天津營口道潮流商圈發現，900米長街道上的44間舖，有17間停業、多間正轉讓；上海則有店主為生計，違法經營色情業，更多小店老闆「跑路」避債。<br />\n<br />\n數據顯示，倒閉小店集中於東部沿海地區，江蘇、廣東、山東的註銷量居全國頭三位。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n美國克林信大學經濟系副教授徐家健表示，疫情底下因生意模式轉變，令結業潮難以避免。數。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/P_Fx6Njseusnd7AFpo7yDLAIFn0=/2101x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HFTCEE3A5NH5FIEEVMX5IZLOGY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FP_Fx6Njseusnd7AFpo7yDLAIFn0%3D%2F2101x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHFTCEE3A5NH5FIEEVMX5IZLOGY.jpg&h=da208dfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【福建】■廈門禾祥西路商業街多間店舖結業。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n網購崛起打擊門市<br />\n<br />\n據「2019年第四次全國經濟普查」，每間個體工商戶可帶動2.37人就業。徐估計，隨着生意轉型，許多來自結業小店的勞動力，會轉到其他行業，例如近年興起的外賣送餐服務；沿海城市的外來勞動人口，也可能會回到受到衝擊較少的地區就業。<br />\n<br />\n據《2020中國個體工商戶洞察報告》，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》記者/澎湃新聞<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/XKKS08lt5jJ1nP5YOFzCbACKcjE=/1575x984/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GECANDMPSFHIBJVQVQ2435K4SA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FXKKS08lt5jJ1nP5YOFzCbACKcjE%3D%2F1575x984%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGECANDMPSFHIBJVQVQ2435K4SA.jpg&h=de5a6ea6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■內地一度提倡地攤經濟促進就業和提高內需。"},{"pid":"8d2ea26eb1393bfc3a3bc51496a8d0794fcbf460","tid":2430841,"uid":59976,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T08:21:30.000Z","msg":"真．黃色經濟圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14ea60ffe444e89e4b87cb8078571493b9a03217","tid":2430841,"uid":35930,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T08:23:05.000Z","msg":"滅一個東莞 仲有千千萬萬個東莞"},{"pid":"d6816b3a55b96ec370a047cb13cb4a4e07c327bd","tid":2430841,"uid":59920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T08:39:47.000Z","msg":"洗浴衝擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.g